Interface IAmGraphSerialController

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAmGraphController
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAmGraphCandleOhlcController
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AmGraphCandleController, AmGraphCandleOhlcController, AmGraphOhlcController, AmGraphSerialController

    public interface IAmGraphSerialController
extends IAmGraphController
    Interface for AmGraphSerialController. This interface contains common properties to graphs used by serial charts but not used by xy charts. Details of AmGraph and its properties in AmCharts API
    Author:
    Iago Fernández Cuñarro
